o expand and to be able to demonstrate to their advertisers that their audience size is growing.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="blue" face="Arial"><u></u>&nbsp;<u></u></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">You’ll get a Radio Plus t-shirt and prizes will be given at the end of the week for the most number of surveys completed.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Radio Plus can be found at the following location:</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><a href="http://www.radioplus.org.uk/contact_us.php" target="_blank">http://www.radioplus.org.uk/<wbr>contact_us.php</a></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">If you’re interested in getting involved in this exciting project please apply to Sarah via sarah.battye@the-challenge.org by <b>5PM 10TH AUGUST.</b></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial, sans-serif" style="font-siz